==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gutturo-
<hw>Gut"tur*o-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A combining form denoting
relation to the throat; <as>as, <ex>gutturo</ex>-nasal, having both a
guttural and a nasal character; <ex>gutturo</ex>-palatal.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gutty</ent>⟦br⟧
